parameters:
Zerachiel: I'm glad everyone is safe
too.

Mel: Could it be that you're an angel
next to me...?

Claudia: I'll kill you if you're an
enemy.

Lala: Wait, wait!! I'm not the enemy,
okay?!

Zerachiel: Lala is being targeted by the
other angels... \c[6]The members of the
choir\c[0] are after her life.

Zerachiel: Yeah, it's going to be a long
story...

Mel: Among the angels, the assault force
that excels in combat is not called the
choir.
Claudia: Why did the choir attack us?

Zerachiel: I don't understand that part.
But...

Zerachiel: I came here to take the lives
of me and Lala. This is the truth.

Lala: If Zerachiel hadn't come, it would
have been dangerous...

Mel: (So Zerachiel and Lala are angels,
huh?)

Mel: The choir members were aiming for
the antidote.

Mel: There shouldn't be a reason to
target such a medicine.

Mel: I don't think I'm unrelated to the
matter of the saint.

Claudia: It would be troublesome if Effy
were to be saved...

Claudia: I wonder if there are people
like that?
Rabi: The one who cursed Lady Effy?

Lala: So it was the evil god Orpheus who
set this up?

Lala: No way, no way! That person is
already dead.

Lala: I don't have the power to move
angels.

Zerachiel: Ever since Effy underwent the
ritual of becoming a saint in the
church, her health has been
deteriorating.

Zerachiel: There was only one person
present during that ritual.

Zerachiel: ...It's the founder of the
Orpheus sect.

Mel: The founder... What kind of person
is that?

Zerachiel: I haven't met them before,
and I don't know them either...

Zerachiel: (But... the answer was in the
Saint's diary)

I received a divine revelation from the
founder.

Be careful, as a young angelic girl
will soon infiltrate the church.

An intruder has appeared in the
church.

She must be the angel that the founder
was talking about. It's surprising to
think that angels actually exist.

The girl's name is apparently called
Zerachiel. It's an unusual name.

Zerachiel: (I infiltrated the church
because of a request from that
person...)

Zerachiel: (I haven't told anyone else,
and there's no one for me to confide
in...)

Zerachiel: (So, the one who leaked
information to the founder was...)

??? : As usual, I will get along with
the humans.

Zerachiel: You are... the first person I
saved in the church...

Lala: It's better not to get close to
that person!!

Lala: ...This person is the Death Angel
Remiel!!

Lala: Among the choir members, she's the
most insane one!!

Remiel: Ahahahaha! I just couldn't help
but laugh too much!!

Remiel: Not only a fake, but even the
traitorous Lala-chan is here too ♪

Remiel: Are you still chasing after the
remnants of that fiery angel?

Remiel: It's futile ♪ The fiery angel
you loved... I've already killed them ♪

Lala: No, that's not true! They're still
alive!

Lala: Ern-sama! There's no way you'll be
killed by the likes of them!!

Remiel: But, you saw it with your own
eyes, didn't you? The moment of your
death at my hands.

Remiel: Those who were there at that
moment, huh? ♪

Remiel: It was such a delight to see
you, poor and pitiful Lala-chan ♪

Remiel: Because of that, I became
depressed and left the choir...

Remiel: It seems that rumors have spread
here too, about searching for the
deceased Archangels ♪
Lala: Be quiet! I won't forgive you...!!

Remiel: I have no intention of
forgiving you, you know?
Remiel: I have no sense of guilt ♪

Remiel: Besides... I have no interest in
you ♪

Remiel: Today's objective is Zerachiel-
chan ♪

Remiel: Zerachiel-chan... Earlier, you
were worried about me, right?

Remiel: Because you're such a soft-
hearted person, your disposal has been
decided, you know?
Remiel: No, how should I address you??

Remiel: A fake of Archangel Sariel-
sama...

Remiel: Homunculus, T-07 type... Angel
Zerachiel-chan ♪
Zerachiel: Eh, what are you saying...

Remiel: You know, you're a homunculus of
Archangel Sariel-sama.

Remiel: I guess you could say I'm only
two years old ♪

Remiel: We angels have decided to start
a war in order to purify the Earth
according to the command of the Supreme
God.

Remiel: For the purpose of purging the
impure human race, you see ♪

Remiel: But you know, angels have low
reproductive ability.

Remiel: Compared to the numerous human
race, our military power is
overwhelmingly lacking.

Remiel: If we continue like this, it
will be necessary to struggle, right?

Remiel: As a fill-in for that, the
production of a homunculus has been
decided.

Remiel: Although they are inferior to
originals, they can be mass-produced and
created infinitely...

Remiel: That's right, Zerachiel-chan ♥
You're a homunculus.

Remiel: Zerachiel-chan, you know, you're
a fake ♪

Zerachiel: Ahaha... What are you
saying... making jokes at a time like
this...

Remiel: Have you seen an angel who looks
just like you in the underground
volcano?

Lala: So, it was you who released the
seal of the Flame Giant!!

Remiel: We released the seal to increase
our fighting power, but...

Remiel: I never expected to be defeated,
hehe ♪

Remiel: But thanks to that, I was able
to create a homunculus ♪

Lala: The giants outside, you all
created them...!!

Remiel: Yes, that's right. You
understand now, don't you?

Remiel: Zerachiel-chan, you're also a
fake.

Zerachiel: B-But! I have memories of the
past too!!

Remiel: For some reason, you have
inherited a part of Sariel-sama's
memories.

Remiel: The supreme god Eden named you
Zerachiel as a rare sample and was
observing your progress.
Remiel: As a result, I failed.

Remiel: As a weapon, you had too much
unnecessary emotions.

Remiel: The supreme god Eden has decided
to dispose of you.

Remiel: That's why I was sent to the
organization, right?

Remiel: So that you can be taken care of
by the organization, hehe ♪

Zerachiel: So, it turns out that
person... Eden-sama was the founder,
huh.
Zerachiel: I have one more question...

Zerachiel: When I first met you, weren't
you being violated by the male priests?
Remiel: Ah, that was me who seduced him.

Remiel: I was asked to keep an eye on
you, but I was so bored ♥

Remiel: They haven't done anything
wrong.

Remiel: But, Zerachiel-chan, you killed
him, didn't you?

Remiel: Just because I had a heart, I
ended up killing unnecessary people,
huh? ♥

Remiel: You have some qualities of a
weapon, don't you? ♪
Zerachiel: Ah, ah... No, it's a lie...
Mel: You scoundrel! Have some shame!!

Remiel: Being lectured by the Demon
Lord's daughter, it's absolutely
hilarious, isn't it? ♥

Remiel: The Demon Lord and their clan
are getting in the way of the plan.

Remiel: I don't hold a grudge against
you, but I'll make sure you die♪
Sachia: I won't let you do that.

Rabi: I would be troubled if you were to
forget about us.
Claudia: Remiel, I understand you well.

Claudia: I can't just let you hurt my
friend.
Lala: Remiel!! I won't let you escape!

Lala: It was shocking to be informed of
the truth, wasn't it?

Lala: I don't think I can fully
understand those feelings.

Lala: So, I'll say it first... I'm
sorry.

Lala: It doesn't matter if you're a
homunculus.

Lala: You are my best friend... the
angel Zerachiel! Isn't that right?
Rabi: I like you, my dear.

Mel: Seeing you trying to make an
antidote for the one who humiliated you,
I fell in love with you.
Mel: You are not a fake.
Mel: You seem more angelic than Remiel.

Claudia: ...If you're feeling down,
we'll cheer you up.
Claudia: I will continue to support you.
Claudia: So, please support us too.
Zerachiel: I am who I am.

Zerachiel: Even if I'm a homunculus,
nothing will change.

Zerachiel: I will give you divine
punishment.

Remiel: Ahahahaha!! I wonder if you can
handle this!

Remiel: Let me introduce you,
Zerachiel-chan♪
Remiel: Same as you... a homunculus♪

Remiel: Well... these dolls don't have
emotions, though♪

Claudia: This... is difficult to
fight...

Sachia: But... we have no choice but to
do it...

Rabi: We'll handle these guys
ourselves!!
Mel: I entrust you with Zerachiel!!

Remiel: Hehe... Come on, Lala-chan, show
me your true power♪

Remiel: Even imposters should entertain
me a little, you know♥

Remiel: Hehe... I suppose it's true that
I do have the blood of Sariel-sama
flowing through me...

Zerachiel: Hmph... I don't know who
Sariel is.

Zerachiel: It seems they underestimated
us and held back... but a match is a
match.
Zerachiel: Shall I have you exit here!!

Remiel: Hehe... That's a consultation I
can't do♥

Lala: Do you think you can escape in
this situation?

???: If it's opponents like you, then
no problem.

Sariel: It's our first time meeting like
this, Zerachiel.

Sariel: I am your original, the
Archangel Sariel-sama.

Remiel: Sariel-sama, that was a close
call♥

Sariel: Remiel is an important comrade
of mine, you know.

Sariel: While I'm at it, let's meet face
to face.
Zerachiel: It's really, just like me...

Sariel: Oh? Are you more surprised than
you thought?

Sariel: Oh, I see. You're surprisingly
delicate, huh?

Sariel: It's hard to believe that I was
a fake.

Sariel: I will break you, but before
that...

Sariel: I have to dispose of the saint
that you want to save, with my own
hands, hehe ♪

Zerachiel: What do you intend to do to
Effy...!!

Sariel: I just want you to become a
sacrifice, you know?

Sariel: They will become nourishment for
the complete revival of that person.
Zerachiel: That person, could it be...

Sariel: Even though you're a fake,
you've already noticed, haven't you?

Sariel: The founder of the Orpheus Cult,
and the one who created you...

Sariel: About the God of Falling Stars,
Lord Eden.

Sariel: Sorry, but there's no time for
chit-chat.
Sariel: I will make you all die.

Sariel: Do you know about the Giant
Tribe of Mist?

Sariel: It refers to the clan that once
fought against the gods and was
defeated.

Sariel: Lord Eden is also the king who
rules over the Giant Tribe.

Sariel: And they are the warriors of the
Giant Tribe♪

Claudia: I'm in trouble. I have very
little magic power left...

Mel: To think they had this much
fighting power remaining...
Rabi: Yes, it's impossible to escape.

Sachia: We have no choice but to give it
our all and try...!!
I'm surrounded by this many giants.
We can't break through on our own, CL.

The giants are attacking all at once,
CL.
Is this the moment of death, CL?

I can't believe I was betrayed by the
person I loved so much, CL.

CL may have wanted to play the role of
a tragic heroine and die.

CL, I want to protect my heart and face
the end.
I think CL had such feelings.
Someone jumped in front of CL.
Sariel: Everyone was cut to pieces.
Sariel: Only pieces of flesh remain.

Azel: Zerachiel-san, I'm glad you made
it in time!

Mel: Azel, you saved me. Let me express
my gratitude.
Mel: However, why are you here?

Azel: I heard that Vahl was attacked, so
I came as reinforcements.
Azel: ...That's just a facade, isn't it?

Azel: I was worried about Lady Mel and
Zerachiel-san, so before I knew it, I
rushed over.

Azel: The other knights are already
engaged in suppressing the angels.

Azel: ...We've almost got them under
control, I think.

Mel: Honestly, you really are
something... as expected...

Azel: There's no need to introduce
yourself.

Sariel: I understand, Remiel. I'm not an
idiot either.

Sariel: This one is warning me about its
dangerous instincts.

Sariel: Fortunately, I have fulfilled
the important role of weakening the
Demon King's forces.

Sariel: I couldn't dispose of my
impostor, but that person will forgive
me too.

Sariel: Zerachiel, I will give you a
prophecy.

Sariel: No matter how hard she tries,
struggles, Effy will die.

Sariel: This is the predetermined
future.
Zerachiel: I won't let that happen.

Zerachiel: I will definitely protect
Effy.

Sariel: Ahaha, you can struggle all you
want.

Sariel: Well then, as a reward, I'll
tell you something interesting.

Sariel: Three days later... We will
attack Logres.

Sariel: You want to save Effy, don't
you? I hope you make it in time.

Mel: Somehow, I managed to get through
it...

Mel: Zerachiel, don't push yourself too
hard.

Zerachiel: There are many things to
think about, but...

Zerachiel: First, we need to help the
people in the town.
Many casualties occurred in the CL town.

The people who were living peacefully in
CL without any sins.

CL became a place where lives were
scattered by the hands of angels.
I didn't want to acknowledge CL.
I had no choice but to accept CL.
Even if CL is fake, I am an angel.

I can't leave the lost lives of CL in
regret.

We need to repay the lives lost in CL
as well.

Because it's CL... I've made up my
mind.

Let's defeat the god Eden, the fallen
star of CL.

Zerachiel: ...Next time, I will
definitely win.
